          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "随心欲那才是一派天真。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "要作个乐逍遥世外之人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "况孩儿每日里闲散成性"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "我的儿休得要把话错论，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不读书焉能够成得贤人？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不枉我守冰霜一片苦心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "二黄原板",
          "musical_style": "二黄原板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "况孩儿每日里闲散成性"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿啊，为娘与你讲了半日，还是照常上学攻书的才是！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿得我的儿德修道进"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孩儿主意已定，从今以后决不到书房去攻书了。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎么你当真的不学？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "当真不学！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然不学？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "果然不学！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唗！为娘三次迁移，几乎把心机用尽，寻得文明的所在，访得真正的明师，指"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "望儿上进攻书，希贤希圣。怎么吾儿厌倦归来，抛弃学业，为娘我再三的相劝，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿是执意不听。哎呀儿呀！你岂不知，仲尼有言：“力不足者，中道而废，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今女画。”只恐你这小奴才就是一个“画”字耳！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "小奴才纵情怀难服教训，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不由娘双眉锁痛恨在心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "只望儿勤学业守道成人。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "叫为娘苦相劝费尽舌唇。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "也罢！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "狠心肠用竹刀把机头断尽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "为择邻娘把那心机用尽"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不料儿在中途抛荒学问"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "老娘亲断机杼所为何情？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "为择邻娘把那心机用尽"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "二黄摇板",
          "musical_style": "二黄摇板",
          "style_family": "二黄",
          "text": "不料儿在中途抛荒学问"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀母亲啊！如今把机头割断，不能织布，岂不是前功枉费了吗？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "儿呀！你也知道为娘我把机头割断不能织布，是前功枉费；你这中途弃学，就"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不是枉费前功么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个！唉！母亲不要生气，孩儿从今以后，改过自新，立定志向，要用心功书，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "努力上进，希贤希圣，定不辜负母亲这一番教子的苦心哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你早要讲出这样的话来，也免得为娘与你生气。来来来，随为娘厨下用饭。正"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "是："
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢讲织布与修身，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "感念慈母教育恩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "但愿吾儿勤学问，"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不期圣贤不休心。"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好一个“不期圣贤不休心”。儿呀！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟轲",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "母亲！"
        },
        {
          "character": "孟母",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "随为娘来呀，哈哈哈……"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（孟母、孟轲同下。）"
        }
